{"tid":2236904,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"特快公屋編配11凶宅出爐 最邪凶廈$1,154超平租","createTime":"2020-10-09T23:36:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-12T07:16:36.000Z","uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"57acba86382c53beca0d05c8b670eea11ca5c8c6","tid":2236904,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T23:36:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/9TNYo74JAsXjNII_gyrO8avVbGw=/1092x661/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MVCMBTSLCRFQ5MYUEO6LKOOHW4.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F9TNYo74JAsXjNII_gyrO8avVbGw%3D%2F1092x661%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMVCMBTSLCRFQ5MYUEO6LKOOHW4.JPG&h=4f0035f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n...<br />\n今年特快公屋編配計劃已於上月10日截止接受申請，房署接獲約6.27萬宗申請，當中約2.83萬宗為二人或以上家庭申請者、約3.44萬宗為一人申請者。翻查資料，過去3年特快公屋編配計劃的申請宗數持續下跌，2017及2018分別收到8.05萬及5.83萬份申請，去年則接獲約5.8萬宗申請，今年申請數字稍為回升。<br />\n房署亦在網頁表明今次特快公屋編配計劃申請人數眾多，不同地區內可選單位數目不一而且有限，無法保證所有申請者均能獲邀揀樓或成功揀選單位。<br />\n<br />\n11凶宅上榜近年最多<br />\n今期名單上有11個單位曾發生兇殺案，屬近年最多，分別在葵涌、屯門、香港仔、深水埗、石硤尾、黃大仙、觀塘、將軍澳及沙田，每月租金由1,154元3,234元不等。<br />\n其中香港仔華富邨華生樓一個單位首次「榜上有名」，該單位在2018年底曾發生倫常慘案，一對年逾六旬夫婦，其中妻子被發現倒斃屋內，頭部有傷痕，丈夫則在屋內上吊身亡；警方懷疑有人用鐵筆擊斃妻子後，畏罪自縊亡。<br />\n...<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201009/ZVW7PSECKNEVVEEG4TNHAVGHBU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201009%2FZVW7PSECKNEVVEEG4TNHAVGHBU%2F&d=6zgGjWaceJ4ICz2LU8gYzlKEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=b13bd033\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201009%2FZVW7PSECKNEVVEEG4TNHAVGHBU%2F&h=f6ad8c8c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201009/ZVW7PSECKNEVVEEG4TNHAVGHBU/</a>"},{"pid":"a32e4cea341060b3397c5a61861ede8cecb95b93","tid":2236904,"uid":173713,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T03:51:12.000Z","msg":"呢啲先正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 轉頭拎個quota去抽居屋"},{"pid":"baabdcbc76f69ca9f258320771a535f44450bf02","tid":2236904,"uid":110832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T03:53:31.000Z","msg":"拎綠表資格啫，都唔係住嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f28536188903d8978f9f266961b96459d048f14","tid":2236904,"uid":215605,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a32e4cea341060b3397c5a61861ede8cecb95b93","tid":2236904,"uid":173713,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T03:51:12.000Z","msg":"呢啲先正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 轉頭拎個quota去抽居屋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T03:57:39.000Z","msg":"要注意的是，獲計劃特快編配公屋的住戶入住該單位3年內不可調遷，期間亦沒有綠表資格，若申請居屋僅能以白表申請，亦須交還公屋單位。"},{"pid":"1578bb0c5811772870fefd7c58b65f9aa95c927d","tid":2236904,"uid":341649,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T04:22:40.000Z","msg":"可唔可以咁講<br />\n比垃圾住完，個單位都變咗垃圾<br />\n連連登仔都彈三彈四<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dae4a07cda4ea5b67963f5a0db601821d9cb8cd","tid":2236904,"uid":7452,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1578bb0c5811772870fefd7c58b65f9aa95c927d","tid":2236904,"uid":341649,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T04:22:40.000Z","msg":"可唔可以咁講<br />\n比垃圾住完，個單位都變咗垃圾<br />\n連連登仔都彈三彈四<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T07:16:36.000Z","msg":"公屋係比垃圾住<br />\n公屋仔跳樓=亂拋垃圾"}]}